  "items": [
    {
      "id": "32843638",
      "text": "কাশীনাথ গাঁওখনৰ ভিতৰতে ধনী মানুহ।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32843638_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32843638",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 5.26
    },
    {
      "id": "32843639",
      "text": "জাপ মাৰি সিহঁতৰ ওপৰত পৰি প্ৰাণবধ কৰে।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32843639_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32843639",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 5.44
    },
    {
      "id": "32843692",
      "text": "এই নম্বৰটো লোৱা আৰু ডাইল কৰা।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32843692_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32843692",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 4.18
    },
    {
      "id": "32869262",
      "text": "এজন আঠ-ন বছৰীয়া ল'ৰা লগ পালে।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32869262_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32869262",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 4.86
    },
    {
      "id": "32850545",
      "text": "তাতে দেউতাই পেছাব কৰিবৰ বাবে টইলেটত সোমাল।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32850545_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32850545",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 7.31
    },
    {
      "id": "32862330",
      "text": "ধেমালি কৰি থাকোঁতে তেওঁলোকক তিনিটা সিংহই আক্ৰমণ কৰে।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32862330_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32862330",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 7.85
    },
    {
      "id": "32862329",
      "text": "ৰত্নৰ বিয়া হয় তাৰ দুবছৰ পাচত।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32862329_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32862329",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 5.08
    },
    {
      "id": "32841095",
      "text": "তেতিয়াৰ দিনত ডটপেন নাছিল।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32841095_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32841095",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 3.82
    },
    {
      "id": "32849994",
      "text": "তাকে নকৰি সি কথাটো মোক ক'লেহেঁতেন।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32849994_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32849994",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 5.04
    },
    {
      "id": "32850485",
      "text": "সকলো যা-যোগাৰ হৈ গ'ল।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32850485_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32850485",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
      "id": "32850549",
      "text": "নিউ য়েৰত গ্ৰীটিং কাৰ্ড দিছিলে।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32850549_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32850549",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 4.25
    },
    {
      "id": "32852686",
      "text": "তাইৰ মুখ এবাৰ দেখিলে কেতিয়াও পাহৰা নেযায়।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32852686_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32852686",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Gaonlia"
      },
      "duration": 8.03
    },
    {
      "id": "32862202",
      "text": "তাই শোৱা ঘৰটো বৰ পুৰণি।",
      "audio": "as/unknown/as_u_32862202_gaonlia.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "32862202",
